        <div class="space-y-4 ">
            <p class="text-lg">Hello again
                <Icon name="emojione:waving-hand" width="20" class="inline-block" />, I am Fazza. A fullstack developer
                from Indonesia
                <Icon name="emojione:flag-for-indonesia" width="20" class="inline-block" />. I love building things,
                especially that is helpful to people.
            </p>
